\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1526546251046{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb]For over 40 years, whilst travelling extensively, I have witnessed poverty in all parts of the world. I have fought against it together with Abb\u00e9 Pierre and also as part of Action Against Hunger. In this world of growing inequalities, I am convinced that each child and each young adult should have the same chances. This will only be possible with the mobilisation of the greatest number of people.[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1526546339518{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb]Break Poverty Foundation is a combination of innovation, research and advocacy in pursuit of the eradication of extreme poverty. We aim to identify and support new solutions and provide the means to develop them on a large scale. We intend to mobilise all efforts in this fight and particularly those of corporations. <strong>We are convinced that building a better world is possible, if everyone gives each other the means to succeed.<\/strong> This is our fight at Break Poverty Foundation. <span style=\"font-size: 26px; color: #00a0e3;\">\u00bb<\/span>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1512641957787{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: right;\">Denis Metzger<\/h4>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\u00a0\u00bb.vc_custom_1627651272823{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\u00a0\u00bb]<\/p>\n<p><em>Credits : Michael Mims, Unsplash.\u00a0<\/em>[\/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row css_animation=\u00a0\u00bb\u00a0\u00bb row_type=\u00a0\u00bbrow\u00a0\u00bb use_row_as_full_screen_section=\u00a0\u00bbno\u00a0\u00bb type=\u00a0\u00bbgrid\u00a0\u00bb angled_section=\u00a0\u00bbno\u00a0\u00bb text_align=\u00a0\u00bbleft\u00a0\u00bb background_image_as_pattern=\u00a0\u00bbwithout_pattern\u0